headline: Energy stock picks: Some traditional (and non-traditional) names
summary: Looking to invest in energy stocks? Tortoise senior portfolio manager and managing director Rob Thummel has a few traditional names, like Cheniere Energy (LNG). But he also has names that you might not even think of as energy-related, such as Seagate (STX).
